14#ifndef RDATA_GENERIC_L32_105_C
15#define RDATA_GENERIC_L32_105_C

17#include <string.h>
18
19#include <isc/net.h>

21#define RRTYPE_L32_ATTRIBUTES (0)
22
23static inline isc_result_t
24fromtext_l32(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
25 isc_token_t token;
26 struct in_addr addr;
27 isc_region_t region;
28
29 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_l32);
30
31 UNUSED(type);
32 UNUSED(rdclass);
33 UNUSED(origin);
34 UNUSED(options);
35 UNUSED(callbacks);
36
37 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
38 false));
39 if (token.value.as_ulong > 0xffffU)
40 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
41 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
42
43 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
44 false));
45
46 if (inet_pton(AF_INET, DNS_AS_STR(token), &addr) != 1)
47 RETTOK(DNS_R_BADDOTTEDQUAD);
48 isc_buffer_availableregion(target, &region);
49 if (region.length < 4)
50 return (ISC_R_NOSPACE);
51 memmove(region.base, &addr, 4);
52 isc_buffer_add(target, 4);
53 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
54}
55
56static inline isc_result_t
57totext_l32(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
58 isc_region_t region;
59 char buf[sizeof("65000")];
60 unsigned short num;
61
62 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_l32);
63 REQUIRE(rdata->length == 6);
64
65 UNUSED(tctx);
66
67 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
68 num = uint16_fromregion(&region);
69 isc_region_consume(&region, 2);
70 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u", num);
71 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
72
73 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
74
75 return (inet_totext(AF_INET, &region, target));
76}
77
78static inline isc_result_t
79fromwire_l32(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
80 isc_region_t sregion;
81
82 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_l32);
83
84 UNUSED(type);
85 UNUSED(options);
86 UNUSED(rdclass);
87 UNUSED(dctx);
88
89 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &sregion);
90 if (sregion.length != 6)
91 return (DNS_R_FORMERR);
92 isc_buffer_forward(source, sregion.length);
93 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sregion.base, sregion.length));
94}
95
96static inline isc_result_t
97towire_l32(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
98
99 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_l32);
100 REQUIRE(rdata->length == 6);
101
102 UNUSED(cctx);
103
104 return (mem_tobuffer(target, rdata->data, rdata->length));
105}
106
107static inline int
108compare_l32(ARGS_COMPARE) {
109 isc_region_t region1;
110 isc_region_t region2;
111
112 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
113 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
114 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_l32);
115 REQUIRE(rdata1->length == 6);
116 REQUIRE(rdata2->length == 6);
117
118 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &region1);
119 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &region2);
120 return (isc_region_compare(&region1, &region2));
121}
122
123static inline isc_result_t
124fromstruct_l32(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
125 dns_rdata_l32_t *l32 = source;
126 uint32_t n;
127
128 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_l32);
129 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
130 REQUIRE(l32->common.rdtype == type);
131 REQUIRE(l32->common.rdclass == rdclass);
132
133 UNUSED(type);
134 UNUSED(rdclass);
135
136 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(l32->pref, target));
137 n = ntohl(l32->l32.s_addr);
138 return (uint32_tobuffer(n, target));
139}
140
141static inline isc_result_t
142tostruct_l32(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
143 isc_region_t region;
144 dns_rdata_l32_t *l32 = target;
145 uint32_t n;
146
147 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_l32);
148 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
149 REQUIRE(rdata->length == 6);
150
151 UNUSED(mctx);
152
153 l32->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
154 l32->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
155 ISC_LINK_INIT(&l32->common, link);
156
157 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
158 l32->pref = uint16_fromregion(&region);
159 n = uint32_fromregion(&region);
160 l32->l32.s_addr = htonl(n);
161 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
162}
163
164static inline void
165freestruct_l32(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
166 dns_rdata_l32_t *l32 = source;
167
168 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
169 REQUIRE(l32->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_l32);
170
171 return;
172}

174static inline isc_result_t
175additionaldata_l32(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
176
177 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_l32);
178 REQUIRE(rdata->length == 6);
179
180 UNUSED(rdata);
181 UNUSED(add);
182 UNUSED(arg);
183
184 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
185}

187static inline isc_result_t
188digest_l32(ARGS_DIGEST) {
189 isc_region_t r;
190
191 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_l32);
192 REQUIRE(rdata->length == 6);
193
194 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
195
196 return ((digest)(arg, &r));
197}

199static inline bool
200checkowner_l32(ARGS_CHECKOWNER) {
201
202 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_l32);
203
204 UNUSED(name);
205 UNUSED(type);
206 UNUSED(rdclass);
207 UNUSED(wildcard);
208
209 return (true);
210}

214

216 REQUIRE(rdata->length == 6);
217
218 UNUSED(rdata);
219 UNUSED(owner);
220 UNUSED(bad);
221

225static inline int
226casecompare_l32(ARGS_COMPARE) {
227 return (compare_l32(rdata1, rdata2));
